{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"386b2a2da7","title":"包围张宣之敌务使不能逃跑","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2e5f7dd4b6","index":0,"year":1948,"month":11,"day":29,"articleId":"386b2a2da7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c7a1af9151","type":"paragraph","text":"包围张宣之敌务使不能逃跑”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"386b2a2da7"},{"id":"3dd379342a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年11月29日）杨、李，杨、罗、职，程、黄中：（一）杨李在包围张官”之敌后，即应迅速完成阻击工事，务使敌人不能逃跑（注意不使敌人黑夜逃跑），以吸引东面数人增援。如张宣敌在你们到达前即已向怀来远跑，你们即应猛道到怀来，务必抓住一部敌人。（二）杨罗取一闻杨李包围了张宜之敌，即应迅速前进包围怀来之敌。（三）程黄仍在现地待命，使敌放心西进增援","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"386b2a2da7"},{"id":"6800332470","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"386b2a2da7"},{"id":"245b4061a2","type":"paragraph","text":"二十九日二十四时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给华北军区第三兵团司令员杨成武和副政治委员兼政治部主任季天燥等的电报。[2]杨、罗、联，指杨得志、罗瑞卿、耿愿，当时分别任华北军区第二东北野战军第二兵团司令员和参课长。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"386b2a2da7"}],"page":{"id":"c1e5a4a869","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"386b2a2da7","start":299,"end":299}}}},"__N_SSG":true}